艺术字生成动画

#创意LOGO视频# #文字动画#

输入艺术字的文字，由文字自由联想画面，生成画面到艺术字的动画



操作说明：
1、输入动画结尾的艺术字的文字内容
2、选择艺术字字体
3、输入想要的艺术字画风
3、输入视频长宽，建议不大于768
4、选择是否开启视频高清放大（默认关闭）



工作流说明:
1、采用Turbo模型保证视频生成速度，请选择对应的Ksample参数，可以选用自己喜欢lightning/turbo/LCM模型
2、视频大小建议512*512/768*768，过大应该会爆显存
3、高清放大耗时预计5-20分钟，一键生成模式默认关闭，本地运行酌情打开
4、本地运行可以增加tile controlnet控制视频文字图像确保生成动画相似度（esheep未找到xl的tile模型）
5、图片的输入词可自行更改，默认仅输入文字
6、暂未支持中文输入，可以本地自行增加translate node后接入text

Text Animation Advertisement Video

#Creative Logo Video# #Text Animation#

Input the text content for artistic lettering, allowing the text to evoke imagery freely, generating animations transitioning to artistic lettering.

Instructions:

1.Input the text content for the artistic lettering at the end of the animation.
2.Select the font_name for the artistic lettering.
3.Input the desired artistic lettering style.
4.Input the video dimensions, recommended not exceeding 768 pixels.
5.Choose whether to enable high-definition scaling for the video (default is disabled).

Workflow Instructions:

1.Utilize the Turbo XL model and LCM to ensure video generation speed. Please select the corresponding Ksample parameter, and you can use your preferred Lightning/turbo/LCM model.
2.Recommended video sizes are 512*512/768*768. Exceedingly large sizes may cause GPU overflow.
3.Ultimate upscale takes an estimated 5-20 minutes. One-click generation mode is disabled by default. Enable it locally as needed.
4.For local runs, you can increase tile controlnet to control the similarity of video text images for generating similar animations .
5.The input words for images can be changed as desired. By default, only text input is supported.
6.Chinese input is not yet supported. You can locally add a translate node before text concatenate.
